Prisa Hires Vocento Director to Head Papers, Confidencial Says

-- B y   M a n u e l   B a i g o r r i
-- 
2011-03-30T07:18:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-30/prisa-hires-vocento-director-to-head-papers-confidencial-says.html
Promotora de Informaciones SA (PRS) , or
Prisa, hired Jose Luis Sainz, general director for  Vocento SA (VOC) ’s
national media, to lead Prisa’s newspaper division,  El
Confidencial  reported today, citing unidentified people in the
industry.  Sainz joined Vocento as general director in June 2009,
after spending 20 years at Prisa, the publisher of El Pais
newspaper, the financial news website said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Manuel Baigorri in Madrid at 
 mbaigorri@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  